ESCORT — SCYTHE (INTERCEPTOR)

Summary/Identity
Smallest Colonial escort hull tuned for high thrust-to-mass and fast response. Interceptor role (engine-heavy). No level gate in our build (ignore the in-game level notice).

Acquisition & Economy

Purchase cost: 600,000 cubits

Operating costs: Boost Cost 1.5 tyl/sec; FTL Cost: 80 tyl/LY

FTL charge/cooldown: 20 s / 35 s

Slot Layout (Medium-size slots)

Weapons: 4

Hull: 2

Engine: 4

Computer: 2

Gun/Launcher/Defensive/Special weapon: 0 (n/a for escorts in our schema; use the generic “Weapons” family)

Role Bonus (Interceptor, systematic—not BSGO-claimed):
Per our project rules, Interceptors receive more engine slots than other roles in the same size class.

Advanced Scythe (design rule): +1 additional Engine slot (total 5), modest energy bump to sustain the extra engine module.

Stat Block (baseline, exact values)
