Hull Recovery: 7.8 /sec

Durability: 14,000

Armor: 25

Critical Defense: 80

Energy / EW / Sensors

Power (capacity): 200

Power Recharge: 10 /sec

Firewall Rating: 100

Emitter Rating: 100

Base DRADIS Range: 1,250 m

Maximum DRADIS Range: 2,500 m

Visual Range: 250 m

FTL

