FTL Charge: 20 s

FTL Cost: 80 tyl/LY

Environmental

Max Radiation Level: 140

Radioactive Decay: 0.9

Radioresistance: 0

Implementation Notes (use these as the coder’s checklist)

Hardpoints/Arcs: 4 weapon mounts; treat as medium-class hardpoints with escort-typical lateral coverage. No special dorsal/ventral coverage rules for Scythe (unlike Glaive).

Interceptor feel: Keep the control response snappy: enforce high turning accel (25 deg/s²) and noticeable drift with modest inertial compensation (50 m/s).

TTK & stamina guardrails: despite low armor, the 7.8/s hull regen lets it reset between skirmishes; ensure sustained boost is limited by 10/s power recharge and 1.5 tyl/s drain.

Advanced upgrade hooks: add +1 Engine slot; increase Power to comfortably support an extra engine mod (+10–20 capacity, +1–2/s recharge), leave survivability nearly unchanged to preserve role identity.

